{"id": 221, "title": "Ticket #221: GSI delegation needs to support Limited Delegation", "description": "<blockquote>\nGSI support in condor should include the ability to perform limited delegation. Anytime a GSI proxy is delegated in Condor, it should be possible to choose between a full and limited proxy. This can be controlled by a config knob and possibly a job attribute. The config knob should be a boolean expression evaluated against the job ad.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2009-Dec-15 10:51:02 by jfrey:</em> <br/>\n\nTicket <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=621\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('621'); return false;\" title=\"Add GSI limited delegation config knob\">#621</a></span> adds config knob DELEGATE_FULL_JOB_GSI_CREDENTIALS as a True/False value that only applies to delegation to a gt2 gram server.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=621\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('621'); return false;\" title=\"Add GSI limited delegation config knob\">#621</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nAdd GSI limited delegation config knob</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Jan-13 21:20</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/9c6a842c20fa17ba00d3819960b311935fb36121\">[25203]</a></span>: document the new behavior of DELEGATE_FULL_JOB_GSI_CREDENTIALS. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=221\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('221'); return false;\" title=\"GSI delegation needs to support Limited Delegation\">#221</a></span>  (By Zach Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2010-Jan-13 21:18</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/4e06c0fd3a70bb90c2df7a003ace420a7f34225f\">[16878]</a></span>: Honor the config knob DELEGATE_FULL_JOB_GSI_CREDENTIALS for all proxy delegations. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=221\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('221'); return false;\" title=\"GSI delegation needs to support Limited Delegation\">#221</a></span>  (By Zach Miller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2010-Jan-28 13:23", "status": "resolved", "created": "2009-Feb-17 17:17", "fixed_version": "2009-Feb-17 17:17", "broken_version": "v070300", "priority": "4", "subsystem": "Security", "assigned_to": "zmiller", "derived_from": "#520", "creator": "zmiller", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}